======================================================================
EULER CHARACTERISTIC OF TOURNAMENTS AND RELATIVE COMPLEXES
======================================================================

======================================================================
n = 4
======================================================================

  Euler characteristic chi = sum (-1)^p beta_p:
    Distribution: {0: 24, 1: 40}

  Omega Euler characteristic = sum (-1)^p dim(Omega_p):
    Distribution: {0: 24, 1: 40}

  Betti profiles (beta_0, beta_1, ..., beta_3):
    (1, 0, 0, 0): 40 (chi=1)
    (1, 1, 0, 0): 24 (chi=0)

